# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Helm chart templates, NOT plain YAML
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These files contain Go-template syntax (`{{ .Values.x }}`) that only
# becomes valid YAML *after* `helm template` renders it. Prettier's YAML
# parser doesn't understand Helm templates and will either fail to parse
# these files or "fix" the `{{ }}` delimiters into something Helm can no
# longer parse (e.g. inserting a space: `{{ .Values.x }}` -> `{ { .Values.x
# } }`). Do not remove this exclusion without also configuring a
# Helm-aware formatter.
infrastructure/kubernetes/base/
infrastructure/kubernetes/templates/

